  "description": "Full FM compound: OscA in supersaw mode (7 voices, 50 cents spread), OscB in FM mode modulating OscA. The supersaw provides a dense frequency cluster; the FM modulation adds spectral sidebands across the whole cluster simultaneously. Drift moves the entire composite through timbral space.",
  "tags": ["odyssey", "supersaw", "fm", "cluster", "drift", "prism", "partials", "transcendental"],
  "tier": "transcendental",
  "guru_bin": {
    "retreat": "ODYSSEY — FM+Drift Compound Migration",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-21",
    "scripture": ["Scripture VII-9: When Seven Voices Drift Together, They Are One Migration"],
    "revelation": "A 7-voice supersaw has 7 slightly different pitch positions. When FM modulates across the supersaw cluster, each of the 7 positions gets unique sidebands. The cluster becomes spectrally rich in a way no single FM voice achieves.",
    "diagnosis": "Path of Partials is the most spectral preset in the Transcendental library — a supersaw cluster receiving FM sidebands from OscB. Drift moves the FM modulator away from the supersaw center, sweeping the sideband distribution across the 7 supersaw voices."
  },
